{
  "title": "Stroomdashboard - overzicht",
  "uid": "stroomdashboard-overzicht",
  "tags": ["stroom", "festival"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": { "from": "now-15m", "to": "now" },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "editie",
        "label": "Editie",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "influxdb" },
        "query": "import \"influxdata/influxdb/schema\"\nschema.tagValues(bucket: \"stroomdata\", tag: \"editie\")",
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": false,
        "multi": false,
        "sort": 3,
        "current": {}
      },
      {
        "name": "kast",
        "label": "Kast",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "influxdb" },
        "query": "import \"influxdata/influxdb/schema\"\nschema.tagValues(bucket: \"stroomdata\", tag: \"kast\")",
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "sort": 1,
        "current": {}
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Per kast - toelichting",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Deze panelen worden automatisch herhaald per kast in `$kast` (bron: MQTT-topic-tags in InfluxDB, niet de webapp-topologie). **Generator-totalen** (som van alleen de direct-gevoede kasten) staan hier bewust niet in, omdat dat kennis van de parent/child-keten uit de webapp vereist — zie `event_dashboard.md` sectie 5 om die handmatig toe te voegen. Alarmdrempels (90% van `rating_a`) zet je ook per paneel handmatig, want die rating staat in de webapp-topologie, niet in InfluxDB."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Totale stroom - $kast",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "repeat": "kast",
      "repeatDirection": "h",
      "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "influxdb" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "amp",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10 }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "influxdb" },
          "query": "from(bucket: \"stroomdata\")\n  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == \"shelly_em\")\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == \"total_current\")\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r.kast == \"${kast}\")\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r.editie == \"${editie}\")",
          "hide": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Stroom per fase - $kast",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "repeat": "kast",
      "repeatDirection": "h",
      "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "influxdb" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "amp",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10 }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "influxdb" },
          "query": "from(bucket: \"stroomdata\")\n  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == \"shelly_em\")\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == \"a_current\" or r._field == \"b_current\" or r._field == \"c_current\")\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r.kast == \"${kast}\")\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r.editie == \"${editie}\")",
          "hide": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
